snippet.title: Double Dog
snippet.description:
DoubleDog (or DDE) is a channel focused on video game history and the nostalgic memories we all associate with them. Video game history is so interesting because it's so recent. Video games are only around 50 years old!

While I hope the videos are informative, entertaining, and half-way educational, I mostly hope you find the retelling of these tales nostalgic, uplifting, and exciting!

- Nat (@doubledognat)
